  "text": "As temporary fault always occurs on overhead HVDC line, once the fault has been cleared, the converter should rebuild the dc line voltage and recover the power transmission. The recovery controls of MMC-HVDC have been fully discussed in the published papers, and the fast recovery control of hybrid MMC, which was discussed in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] , is employed in the S2L-MDCC.",
